ru.inp.stackexchange.api

Class SEGatewayClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.inp.stackexchange.api.SEGatewayClient

  • public class SEGatewayClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Stack Exchange API gateway client. Is used to send a request and read the response. Should be built by using methods set* and build(). Can be fully created by the SEGatewayClientFactory.
